RailsBrakeman is an online service to find security issues in your Rails
projects.

1. Create an account on rails-brakeman.com (just sign in with GitHub)
2. Create a repository on rails-brakeman.com
3. Enter your token
  - the token which you can find on repository edit page on rails-brakeman.com
4. Enter your rails_brakeman_url if you deploy the proxy on your own server
5. Check the "Active" checkbox and click "Update Settings"

For more details about RailsBrakeman, go to https://rails-brakeman.com

